{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/start.png?t=1738691816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Forsaken Lands</strong>, immerse yourself in a world full of captivating stories. Explore the mysteries of an ancient race hiding in dark forests, find the Great Necromancer, and uncover his secrets. And, of course, an epic battle with the Gods in the heavens awaits you. To unravel all the mysteries of the <strong>Forsaken Lands</strong>, you'll need to carefully assemble a team of heroes, develop their skills, and strengthen their unit </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/Fight.gif?t=1738691816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/feat__3_.png?t=1738691816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Experience different story campaigns</strong>, each dedicated to its own unique tale in the world of the Forsaken Lands:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Assemble a team of three heroes</strong>, choosing from many unique characters, and adapt your playstyle to your preferences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock new cards and relics</strong>, changing your strategy on the fly </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Battle not only regular enemies but also their enhanced versions</strong>. Then challenge powerful bosses \u2014 each requiring a special approach</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Test yourself in roguelite mode</strong>, where each playthrough is unique, and battles offer unexpected surprises</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/Hero_Selection.gif?t=1738691816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/worldheroes.png?t=1738691816\" /> <strong>Lead a squad of three heroes</strong>, each with their own deck of cards, special skills, and playstyle. As you progress, your heroes will develop, acquiring new cards, abilities, and customization options</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/lake_dialog__1_.gif?t=1738691816\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Game with a Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tired of the same old characters? No problem! Swap out one, two, or all three heroes, experimenting with the boldest combinations. But remember: in every story, the main thing is the story itself, and the heroes are merely instruments for its embodiment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/Map_Narrative.gif?t=1738691816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/demo.png?t=1738691816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the current demo of Forsaken Lands you can find:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>3 unique heroes</strong>, each with their gameplay style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Over 50 cards</strong>: 30+ cards for each hero and 15+ neutral cards to create the perfect deck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>10 types of enemies</strong> with different variations, presenting new challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>2 epic bosses</strong>, each requiring a unique strategy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Events</strong> with surprises adding depth to your adventure</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/Card_Shop.gif?t=1738691816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the future, we plan to add a <strong>cooperative mode</strong> so you can share each adventure with two of your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/end__2_.png?t=1738691816\" /> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738691816","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/page.bg.jpg?t=1738691816","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/9948b187b64634a4d2f9d35f217235259375597b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738691816","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/9948b187b64634a4d2f9d35f217235259375597b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738691816","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3265090,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464640/extras/start.png?t=1738691816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Forsaken Lands</strong>, immerse yourself in a world full of captivating stories. Explore the mysteries of an ancient race hiding in dark forests, find the Great Necromancer, and uncover his secrets. And, of course, an epic battle with the Gods in the heavens awaits you. To unravel all the mysteries of the <strong>Forsaken Lands</strong>, you'l